Package group2.shah.mili.zuhlke.matt.emoviecon

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AboutUsActivity
    EMovieCon activity used to start the about us activity
    EMovieCon
    EMovieCon Class to hold a movie with the basic information we plan to present
    EMovieConActivity
    EMovieConActivity Class to start every activity that extends this class with the header and navigation menu
    MainActivity
    Main Activity started first after the splash screen Contains large image buttons defined onclick actions to start activity intents
    MovieDetails
    Movie Details Activity started after selecting a movie from the recycler view
    MovieRecyclerAdapter
    Recycler adapter for the viewholder for a movie scroll Recycler adapter is the best choice since it loads three at a time and the Lists can be 800+ in size
    PlayingNowActivity
    Playing now activity that extends EMovieConActivity to add menu functionality Grabs movies in the playing now category in TheMovieDB
    SettingsActivity
    Settings activity that extends EMovieConActivity to add menu functionality Adds Setting for page query count.
    SplashActivity
    Splash activity that shows the EMovieCon logo and start screen and startup activities like loading lists
    TheMovieDBWrapper
    Wrapper class that interfaces with TheMovieDB all calls and parsing should come from this class
    UpcomingActivity
    UpComing activity that extends EMovieConActivity to add menu functionality Grabs movies in the playing now category in TheMovieDB
